data.title: X. Fliegerkorps
data.text:
Kommandierender General:

Gen Hans Geisler, 2.10.39 - 31.8.42

Gen Bernhard Kühl (acting), 3.6.40 - 20.9.40

Gen Otto Hoffmann von Waldau, 31.8.42 - 31.12.42

GenLt Alexander Holle, 1.1.43 - 22.5.43

Gen Martin Fiebig, 22.5.43 - 1.9.44

Chef des Stabes:

Obstlt Martin Harlinghausen, 1.11.39 - 31.3.41

GenLt Ulrich Kessler (acting), 25.4.40 - 21.5.40

GenLt Günther Korten, 1.4.41 - 3.42

Oberst Sigismund Freiherr von Falkenhausen, 1.4.42 - 3.43

Maj Eckard Christian, 8.3.43 - 2.6.43

GenMaj Walter Boenicke, 6.43 - 6.1.44

?

Formed 2.10.39 in Hamburg as 10. Flieger-Division.

On 2.10.39 renamed X. Fliegerkorps. In 3.44 part of the Stab was used to form Kommandierende General der Deutschen Luftwaffe in Griechenland. Disbanded 5.9.44.
